snippet.title: Fatal Frame 4 Trailer (English) (HD)
snippet.description:
DISCLAIMER:Fatal Frame 4 does not belong to me. It belongs to Tecmo and Nintendo.

Hey guys soon I'm gonna upload fatal Frame 4 Walkthrough and many other walkthroughs.This a scene at the beginning of the chapter 1 Out of Tune.These Videos are gonna be full HD.For the sample,I've posted this trailer. Problem is that the game runs slow on my pc and some cutscenes are extremely laggy, but that's caused by the patch and I can't fix it.I'm trying to fix it.Thanx to Tempus for dubbing the awesome game in English.I've once completed the game and hence you'll see Ruka and others in different costumes.  

Comment and subscribe for more videos.
